parameters.name: GroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the domain name group.

parameters.name: KeyWord
parameters.description: The keyword for the query in "%KeyWord%" mode. The keyword is not case-sensitive.

parameters.name: Lang
parameters.description: The language in which you want the values of some response parameters to be returned. These response parameters support multiple languages.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number to return. The page number starts from **1**. Default value: **1**.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return per page. Maximum value: **100**. Default value: **20**.

parameters.name: StartDate
parameters.description: The start time for the query. Format: **YYYY-MM-DD**

parameters.name: Type
parameters.description:
The type of object of which you want to query operation logs. Valid values:

*   domain: domain name
*   slavedns: secondary Domain Name System (DNS)

parameters.name: endDate
parameters.description: The end time for the query. Format: **YYYY-MM-DD**
